This hit by Gordon Lightfoot was the 145th #1 song on what is now the Billboard's Adult Contemporary charts. It also hit #5 on the Top 40 charts, #1 in Canada and on their AC charts, #19 in New Zealand, #28 in Australia, and #30 in the United Kingdom.
